You could also see if it's drawing an appropriate amount of current: 2.5A -
3.5A

>But with the key on and the cover off the AFM, I
> should be able to hear the Fuel Injection pump go on and pressurize the
> system, when I move the dial inside the AFM.  This does not happen.  So is
> it a wiring issue? Fuse somewhere?

The double relay activates the pump via the AFM switch. Check those
connections.

